### Posts - examples

### List posts
GET http://localhost:3000/posts
Accept: application/json

### Get post by id
GET http://localhost:3000/posts/6e316c67-f02b-4135-985b-48b4d4dd198c
Accept: application/json

### Create a post (protected) — include photo URLs inline
POST http://localhost:3000/posts
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJiM2Y5OTA1Ny1mZTA2LTQ5NGQtYTQwNi02ODdkNDJiMzU1ZDciLCJpYXQiOjE3NjEzNjg2MDJ9.GZBHHit-Mjo_d7rKDhpTpHjffAuCZB3P1syGjWW1Iso
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "type": "BOTH",
  "text": "There is trash near the park",
  "pinId": "c70df4a4-81d4-4897-8bbb-66336c370467",
  "photos": [
    { "url": "https://example.com/img1.jpg", "isBefore": true },
    { "url": "https://example.com/img2.jpg", "isBefore": false }
  ]
}

### Update a post (protected)
